<h2 id="transmission">Transmission</h2>
<p><em>Transmission</em> is a minimal BitTorrent client, which serves its purpose very well. So many BitTorrent clients are bloated and unsuable, <em>Transmission</em> keeps it simple. [<a href="https://transmissionbt.com">https://transmissionbt.com</a>]</p>

<h2 id="iterm2">iTerm2</h2>
<p>Yes, <em>iTerm2</em> is a terminal emulator, but somehow itâ€™s a GUI tool. Itâ€™s the best replacement for the stock macOS <em>Terminal.app</em>. [<a href="https://www.iterm2.com">https://www.iterm2.com</a>]</p>

<h2 id="tunnelblick">Tunnelblick</h2>
